channel.title: I absoutely neeed help with this
channel.description:
Hey guys, so yesterday my browsers stopped working after my AVG restarted my computer after removing a threat. My internet is connected and my Skype and things still work. I have tried setting up a new DNS but no luck with that, I have disabled my firewall and no luck, flushed my dns and no luck, restarted my modem repeatedly. I have tried everything but I cannot figure it out. I am in need of someone who really knows what they are doing to help me out. Please pm me if you know what to do. I keep seeing that I need to get MALWAREBYTES or whatever but I cannot do that because I can't open web pages. Pleasee help.
---FIXED--- Just ended up buying a new computer lol. Needed one anyways :P
